1ueYIkqBBQ6zoeQ">Tặng Kim Lệ Thuỵ kỳ 2 - 贈金勵睡其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90o%C3%A0n/author-MvIfk3uwGuMtJiglF2Flng">Trần Đoàn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Thi%C3%AAn-v%C3%A2n-v%E1%BA%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-gian/poem-ugRfi601e7To8GsJFZCPtQ">Thiên vân vạn thuỷ gian - 千雲萬水間</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-13-Kh%C3%A1ch-x%C3%A1-ng%E1%BB%99-v%C5%A9-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-OCGUnHKaSd8nPxH6zC271w">Thủ 13 - Khách xá ngộ vũ cảm hoài - 首１３</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-JXVRPKJDWypc2_dzSZu2GA">Thu nguyệt ngẫu thành - 秋月偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
